81
00:08:08,157 --> 00:08:15,189
But the ruler in Hobbes’s opinion must come from the power that is given by the people.

82
00:08:16,030 --> 00:08:18,659
Not by force.

83
00:08:20,409 --> 00:08:21,850
I didn’t ask.

84
00:08:24,486 --> 00:08:26,486
If you want to answer that much,

85
00:08:27,493 --> 00:08:29,866
tell me what Montesquieu’s principle is.

86
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:32,815
The separation of powers into three branches,

87
00:08:33,823 --> 00:08:37,788
The Legislative Branch, the Executive Branch, and the Judicial Branch.

88
00:08:37,789 --> 00:08:38,875
What about John Locke?

89
00:08:41,941 --> 00:08:43,289
You can’t answer it.

90
00:08:50,923 --> 00:08:56,999
Freedom and liberty are fundamental human rights that all humans are born with.

91
00:08:58,017 --> 00:08:59,551
That’s his ideal.

92
00:09:04,222 --> 00:09:06,222
You’re interesting, Ayan.

93
00:09:08,864 --> 00:09:14,288
Having a student like you in class makes the class a lot livelier.

94
00:09:15,395 --> 00:09:18,420
I guess we need to do questions and answers like this more often.

95
00:09:22,565 --> 00:09:26,894
What are the synonyms of the word ‘Phra Arthit?’ (The sun)

96
00:09:27,432 --> 00:09:28,357
Ayan.

97
00:09:29,825 --> 00:09:33,881
Suriya, Tinakorn, Tiwakorn.

98
00:09:33,881 --> 00:09:36,308
And the synonyms of ‘The moon?’

99
00:09:36,607 --> 00:09:38,141
Ayan, answer it.

100
00:09:38,506 --> 00:09:43,185
Is substance X's boiling point higher than that of substances Y and Z?

101
00:09:44,235 --> 00:09:45,163
Yes, it is.

102
00:09:45,668 --> 00:09:48,483
And why is substance X soluble in water?

103
00:09:50,001 --> 00:09:51,121
Can I answer that?

104
00:09:52,985 --> 00:09:54,377
So, Ayan?

105
00:09:57,869 --> 00:10:00,000
The teachers were so harsh on Aye today.

106
00:10:00,401 --> 00:10:01,376
Right.

107
00:10:02,394 --> 00:10:03,835
I laughed at first.

108
00:10:04,037 --> 00:10:06,153
He’s so cocky. I thought he deserved it.

109
00:10:07,494 --> 00:10:09,564
But the old lads wouldn’t stop.

110
00:10:09,955 --> 00:10:11,769
Now I feel guilty I laughed.

111
00:10:12,484 --> 00:10:17,815
