112
00:10:23,099 --> 00:10:24,074
I don’t know.

113
00:10:25,814 --> 00:10:27,604
You guys go ahead. I’ll catch up with you.

114
00:10:28,443 --> 00:10:29,164
Yeah.

115
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:35,334
Hi, Akk.

116
00:10:35,683 --> 00:10:36,719
