128
00:11:16,045 --> 00:11:16,973
What’s the matter with you?

129
00:11:18,957 --> 00:11:20,957
Or you’ve been brainwashed by Ayan too?

130
00:11:23,544 --> 00:11:24,468
No, sir.

131
00:11:25,097 --> 00:11:25,893
Akk.

132
00:11:26,812 --> 00:11:29,348
We have Suppalo guidelines and rules to follow.

133
00:11:30,001 --> 00:11:30,825
Keep that in mind.

134
