You knew about it, didn’t you?

139
00:11:54,130 --> 00:11:54,929
About what?

140
00:11:55,524 --> 00:11:57,314
About the teachers picking on me.

141
00:11:58,411 --> 00:11:59,464
Aye.

142
00:11:59,860 --> 00:12:02,391
I have no clue what you’re doing.

143
00:12:02,956 --> 00:12:04,061
But if I were you,

144
00:12:05,389 --> 00:12:06,284
I’d stop.

145
00:12:12,099 --> 00:12:13,540
- Or…
- I won’t stop.

146
00:12:53,656 --> 00:12:55,656
Ayan.

