00:13:53,324 --> 00:13:54,835
You keep staring at my face.

156
00:13:56,413 --> 00:13:57,337
Nonsense.

157
00:14:17,280 --> 00:14:18,535
You knew about it, didn’t you?

158
00:14:20,831 --> 00:14:21,576
About what?

159
00:14:23,279 --> 00:14:25,135
About the teachers picking on me.

160
00:14:30,916 --> 00:14:32,036
How would I know?

161
00:14:36,198 --> 00:14:36,827
Yeah?

162
00:14:41,609 --> 00:14:42,999
This is not you at all.

163
00:14:45,326 --> 00:14:47,039
You normally don’t yield easily.

164
00:14:48,503 --> 00:14:50,503
Why did you let them do that much to you?

165
00:14:58,017 --> 00:14:59,802
It’s the only way to know

166
00:15:02,361 --> 00:15:06,406
how your school dealt with someone who disagreed.

167
00:15:08,730 --> 00:15:09,760
Who are you talking about?

168
00:15:10,639 --> 00:15:11,968
Who did this school deal with?

169
00:15:13,744 --> 00:15:14,494
No one.

170
00:15:15,050 --> 00:15:16,228
I’m just saying.

171
00:15:16,970 --> 00:15:17,889
Tell me.

172
00:15:18,248 --> 00:15:19,203
Stop talking.

173
00:15:19,786 --> 00:15:20,620
I’m tired.

174
00:16:16,308 --> 00:16:18,452
You won’t be so mean to me too, right?

175
00:16:58,862 --> 00:17:01,759
(I don’t want it anymore. You take it.)

176
00:17:24,107 --> 00:17:25,022
Yes, Mom.

177
00:17:26,403 --> 00:17:27,488
Yes.

178
00:17:28,790 --> 00:17:29,769
Sure.

179
