- I won’t stop.

204
00:18:47,306 --> 00:18:47,964
Fine.

205
00:18:49,417 --> 00:18:51,172
Be careful then.

206
00:18:52,811 --> 00:18:53,521
Bye now.

207
00:18:54,811 --> 00:18:55,688
Thua.

208
00:18:57,249 --> 00:18:58,587
Don’t forget our appointment this Sat.

209
00:19:00,883 --> 00:19:01,545
Um.

210
00:19:07,323 --> 00:19:09,251
Why am I even doing this?

211
00:19:09,479 --> 00:19:11,874
Just do it. It’s one way to help our school.

212
00:19:17,959 --> 00:19:18,833
Follow him.

213
00:19:19,299 --> 00:19:20,425
Who do you think he’s meeting?

214
00:19:20,674 --> 00:19:21,956
The World Remembers gang?

215
00:19:23,105 --> 00:19:25,213
Maybe he’s afraid of being watched in school.

216
00:19:25,759 --> 00:19:27,041
That’s why he’s meeting them outside.

217
00:19:27,897 --> 00:19:29,897
I think they’re planning the next protest.

218
00:19:30,331 --> 00:19:33,461
Planning the protest in a coffee shop?

219
00:19:34,151 --> 00:19:35,285
Isn’t it weird?

220
00:19:36,774 --> 00:19:38,178
