00:20:06,706 --> 00:20:07,731
I think they’ve learned the lesson now.

224
00:20:10,117 --> 00:20:13,699
If nobody messes with their heads again, things should be peaceful.

225
00:20:14,885 --> 00:20:15,949
No one will.

226
00:20:16,333 --> 00:20:18,082
Ayan was done pretty bad.

227
00:20:20,285 --> 00:20:21,540
But let me guess.

228
00:20:22,239 --> 00:20:24,013
The gang was dealt with already.

229
00:20:24,418 --> 00:20:27,141
The teachers’ next target should be Aye.

230
00:20:28,151 --> 00:20:29,857
That method won't work.

231
00:20:32,597 --> 00:20:33,670
Why did you hit the table?

232
00:20:35,070 --> 00:20:36,494
What method do you suggest?

233
00:20:38,334 --> 00:20:39,431
I don’t know yet.

234
00:20:39,997 --> 00:20:44,165
But if we know why he joined this school, we might know how to handle him.

235
00:20:50,012 --> 00:20:50,781
I know it.

236
00:20:51,413 --> 00:20:53,954
We found nothing because we only follow him inside school.

237
00:20:54,171 --> 00:20:55,939
What if we follow him outside school?

238
00:20:59,027 --> 00:21:00,937
Like when you went to his house yesterday?

239
00:21:01,253 --> 00:21:01,963
Yes.

240
00:21:02,240 --> 00:21:05,121
But we’re following him every day, weekdays and weekends.

241
00:21:05,273 --> 00:21:06,322
What about public holidays?

242
00:21:06,619 --> 00:21:07,480
That too.

243
00:21:10,648 --> 00:21:12,083
Are you guys free this weekend?

244
00:21:13,582 --> 00:21:17,050
