254
00:21:40,999 --> 00:21:41,747
Please.

255
00:21:42,280 --> 00:21:44,280
Kan, my dear friend.

256
00:21:46,697 --> 00:21:47,703
Wat, my beloved friend.

257
00:22:07,010 --> 00:22:07,715
