262
00:22:19,819 --> 00:22:23,404
People won’t stop sharing about it in the parents' group chat.

263
00:22:23,717 --> 00:22:25,717
You don’t take any part in it, do you?

264
00:22:25,717 --> 00:22:28,514
The protest happened before I joined.

265
00:22:29,624 --> 00:22:31,059
Because the system is broken.

266
00:22:32,269 --> 00:22:36,075
