267
00:22:36,075 --> 00:22:36,761
Aye,

268
00:22:37,058 --> 00:22:39,058
I think this is too risky.

269
00:22:40,050 --> 00:22:41,192
Stop it.

270
00:22:41,417 --> 00:22:43,756
Don’t get involved with it anymore. Let it go.

271
00:22:44,284 --> 00:22:45,129
No.

272
00:22:45,739 --> 00:22:47,707
I won’t let Uncle Di die for nothing.

273
00:23:01,764 --> 00:23:03,619
